comments: Irving (BKN) is bracing for the contact from Smith (IND) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Mathurin (IND) straddles the lane line and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Smith (IND) legally contests Irving's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Watanabe (BKN) is moving alongside Mathurin's (IND) path and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Watanabe's (BKN) left hand comes down slightly and brushes Mathurin's (IND) off arm before he immediately retreats his arm into a vertical position.  The contact is marginal.
Haliburton (IND) and O'Neale (BKN) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
O'Neale (BKN) and Haliburton (IND) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Hield (IND) legally contests Irving's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Smith (IND) is already in Irving's (BKN) path and marginal contact occurs as the defenders switch.
Harris (BKN) brings his hand towards Haliburton's (IND) front and marginal contact occurs as Haliburton dribbled behind his back.
Harris (BKN) is moving alongside Haliburton's (IND) path to the basket, and marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Harris (BKN) is retreating his arm into a vertical position and absorbs the marginal contact from Haliburton (IND) during his upward shooting motion.
Irving (BKN) clamps and holds Smith's (IND) right arm, which affects Smith's ability to bring two hands to the rebound.
Irving's (BKN) left foot comes down out of bounds while he is still in possession of the ball.
Durant (BKN) and Duarte (IND) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Durant (BKN) goes to, rather than through, Duarte's (IND) space and marginal contact occurs as the two come together at the start of Durant's dribble in the post.
Smith (IND) fails to fully clear the lane and is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Hield (IND) brushes Irving's (BKN) off arm and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Smith (IND) is already in O'Neale's (BKN) path and is firming up when contact occurs.

Watanabe (BKN) is moving alongside Haliburton's (IND) path and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.  Additionally, Watanabe brings his hand slightly forward, and marginal contact occurs with Haliburton's wrist after he has released his shot attempt.
Haliburton (IND) extends his arms into Durant's (BKN) body and dislodges him from his legally obtained position.
Haliburton (IND) gathers the ball on his right foot and does not take more than two steps after his gather before he passes the ball.
Durant (BKN) legally contests Haliburton's (IND) jump shot attempt.
Hield (IND) and Harris (BKN) come together at the same spot while the ball is in the air and marginal contact occurs as Hield releases away to secure the rebound.
Harris (BKN) legally contests Hield's (IND) jump shot attempt.
Mathurin (IND) lowers his shoulder into Irving's (BKN) chest and initiates contact that dislodges Irving from his legally obtained defensive position.
Multiple angles reviewed.  There is no clear and conclusive camera angle that shows if Irving (BKN) makes contact with the baseline when he gains possession of the ball.
